{"tid":23324,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人想去尼泊爾行山","createTime":"2016-12-05T01:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T03:38:28.000Z","uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f382c7fbbc1b99f20f8578ea5354ad7063503493","tid":23324,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"想去一次10日左右嘅登山團，有無巴打有經驗?<br />\n因為身邊無乜朋友可以組到團,<br />\n香港/當地團一個人跟有無介紹?<br />\n求指教!感謝[img][/img]"},{"pid":"b9141aa08a557e2036117e6391052f5dd256fb0c","tid":23324,"uid":35520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實最好都係幾個人share導遊同擔夫錢。<br />\n一個人請一個又係咁貴，四個人請一個又係咁貴。"},{"pid":"b484ef23df6acbffec64b58c7626d18840368f7d","tid":23324,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:24:35.000Z","msg":"琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行"},{"pid":"9e73cbc89ae7e51e55c76b2e0404ecdd549d7ade","tid":23324,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee98862700e1b313ca620610ee72b137a91ca890","tid":23324,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我行左七日<br />\n都好撚悶<br />\n十日應該仲撚悶<br />\n<br />\n落左山有得上網果下<br />\n你feel到個腦d安多汾爆哂出來<br />\n<br />\nbtw 值得一試"},{"pid":"3c975d97bde3aee4730d72ab28ea40d4c378e99f","tid":23324,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"搵挑夫好撚on9<br />\n當人奴隸咁洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去行山就是煅練嘛<br />\n<br />\n導遊我都無用<br />\n但係呢 見到人地d導遊都幾好人<br />\n當我行唔郁佢地會鼓勵我<br />\n好正"},{"pid":"42daf6d24dbc50d2860e40d6f611e2cde33dab68","tid":23324,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山上樣樣都係錢<br />\nWifi沖涼食水充電全部都要錢<br />\n上到越高就開始冇肉食同冇上網<br />\n<br />\n其實體能上唔難<br />\n如果你擔心安全問題<br />\n可以路上搵伴<br />\n我都有見過好多女仔自己一個行<br />\n<br />\nAbc好多時都係叢林中穿梭<br />\n如果你一心想睇景可以行ebc"},{"pid":"1cb60e0d74598b6564b2de5745b9fed953296bc8","tid":23324,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵挑夫好撚on9<br />\n當人奴隸咁洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去行山就是煅練嘛<br />\n<br />\n導遊我都無用<br />\n但係呢 見到人地d導遊都幾好人<br />\n當我行唔郁佢地會鼓勵我<br />\n好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都唔諗住搵挑夫，自己拎野先有意思！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n７日都得　仲好！因為將會有１０日假期～<br />\n我應該可以慢慢來"},{"pid":"fda2b80cc1dc1c83d77637388372e0d2048b488b","tid":23324,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山上樣樣都係錢<br />\nWifi沖涼食水充電全部都要錢<br />\n上到越高就開始冇肉食同冇上網<br />\n<br />\n其實體能上唔難<br />\n如果你擔心安全問題<br />\n可以路上搵伴<br />\n我都有見過好多女仔自己一個行<br />\n<br />\nAbc好多時都係叢林中穿梭<br />\n如果你一心想睇景可以行ebc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n２路線都想行～當然今次只行一條，所以EBC入門為佳?"},{"pid":"b3b0e6be3abf4ee9656af3afeeda8ad901e560fe","tid":23324,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:46:57.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇 Telegram"},{"pid":"918b60be8084fafd3033c72199c93235c2e44d82","tid":23324,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"有興趣行"},{"pid":"d4c5ef093de164142c3ff4502c66d7c147a7098a","tid":23324,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"ebc 係高難度 好似要十幾廿日<br />\nabc 中難度 七至十日<br />\npoon hill 四日行完"},{"pid":"bc2559b85c94752dc15c250900de35348eb1a132","tid":23324,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>琴日行完尼泊爾abc<br />\n正常就10日行完<br />\n一個人去冇問題 唔洗挑夫加導遊<br />\n可以路上搵人結伴同行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享多Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山上樣樣都係錢<br />\nWifi沖涼食水充電全部都要錢<br />\n上到越高就開始冇肉食同冇上網<br />\n<br />\n其實體能上唔難<br />\n如果你擔心安全問題<br />\n可以路上搵伴<br />\n我都有見過好多女仔自己一個行<br />\n<br />\nAbc好多時都係叢林中穿梭<br />\n如果你一心想睇景可以行ebc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n２路線都想行～當然今次只行一條，所以EBC入門為佳?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEbc個重點係珠穆朗瑪峰<br />\n個景好壯觀<br />\n反之亦然係比較難<br />\n<br />\n景色方面abc相比之下就有點失色<br />\n2條都係熱門路線<br />\nAbc係入門級<br />\n<br />\n你可以行曬abc加poon hill<br />\n7-8日可以行曬"},{"pid":"d63bc7a0bbacb8644bb2a0257d25659f54e930a8","tid":23324,"uid":23858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"就算行abc 你都唔好預咁忟水<br />\n你去到尼泊爾首都之後未必可以即刻去到山腳起點<br />\n因為首都同起點都有一段距離<br />\n一係撘半個鐘內陸機，一係撘6個鐘巴士<br />\n<br />\n我個次去都要第二日6點幾撘內陸機去山腳<br />\n有去程就有回程，呢d時間都幾襟計。<br />\n<br />\n另外途中識到朋友一齊行，咁佢有請guide<br />\n有時book lodge 都會幫我book 埋，所以我每晚都有比tips佢<br />\n<br />\n係尼泊爾d錢好好洗，物價好低，<br />\n但係市區一定要講價<br />\n<br />\n利伸，上年自己一個上abc,6日行完"},{"pid":"cdba06cc2385ed9db730dddc0b461295bd292cb0","tid":23324,"uid":23858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"同埋我都係係高登睇到李小明個post 先有勇氣出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4ce23c01f7936e1810c005ef517351ab3821f9","tid":23324,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"打算下年四月尾至五月頭行EBC，結伴乎？"},{"pid":"d468ee4da6ec7aec8845d98f68deff8c9f7104d4","tid":23324,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"睇左孤高之人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989d5d3db685d220f2756af18add15a02192254f","tid":23324,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打算下年四月尾至五月頭行EBC，結伴乎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更正，係ACT（安娜普爾納大環線），行12～14日"},{"pid":"357f6ce8f0db2e5698c947f145d0395bb176c2b9","tid":23324,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"有興趣 可以結伴"},{"pid":"06dca36bd90ff5a7f6c904c18e182c4b788e0f4b","tid":23324,"uid":38474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"有無人行ebc但無用導遊？ <br />\n我好有興趣去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f7eb452c48f87b34875ab679360a3015eae609","tid":23324,"uid":33034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"有興趣想去 點搵樓主？"},{"pid":"7d4a7b77ffffc7f7270b71f533d754a402e1176c","tid":23324,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f382c7fbbc1b99f20f8578ea5354ad7063503493","tid":23324,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"想去一次10日左右嘅登山團，有無巴打有經驗?<br />\n因為身邊無乜朋友可以組到團,<br />\n香港/當地團一個人跟有無介紹?<br />\n求指教!感謝[img][/img]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"開咗group，入嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}